testNG
Benefits of testNg:
 - it has lots of annotations which you can use to implement your test cases
 - all the tests can be grouped and prioritized through testNg
 - parallely run your tests in different threads
 - data parameterization
 - it produces HTML reports
 
TestNg XML - which you can use to run your program
1. annotations
    @Test - to let java know it is a testing method